name: BMO Long Short US Equity ETF
longDescription: The BMO Long Short US Equity ETF has been designed to provide long-term capital appreciation with attractive risk-adjusted returns, by taking long and short positions in primarily US equities. The strategy will seek to buy fundamentally strong, attractively valued stocks and sell short companies that are not as highly rated within the fund's model. The BMO Long Short US Equity ETF has been designed to provide longterm capital appreciation.
